z^2+2iz-1+2i
(z+i)^2-1-1+2i
(z+i)^2 = 2-2i
a^2-b^2 = 2, 2ab = -2, a^2+b^2 = \sqrt(8)
z^2+2iz-1+2i=0
z^2+2iz-1+2i=(z+i)^2+2i=0
(z+i)^2=-2i\\ z+i=\pm(1-i)\Rightarrow\quad z=\{-1,1-2i\}
z^2+2 i z-1 = (z+i)^2
(z+i)^2=-2 i = 2 \, e^{i 3\pi/2} \implies z+i = \begin{cases} \sqrt{2} \, e^{i 3 \pi/4} \\   \sqrt{2} \, e^{-i \pi/4}\end{cases} 
z=-1
z=1-2 i
\star
z^2+2iz+(2i-1) = 0
 \begin{align} z & = \frac12\left(-2i\pm \sqrt{(2i)^2 - 4(2i-1)}\right)\\ & =\frac12\left(-2i\pm \sqrt{-8i}\right) \\ & = \frac12\left(-2i\pm\sqrt{2i}\sqrt{-4}\right) \tag{$\star$}\\ & = \frac12\left(-2i\pm(1+i)(2i)\right) \\ & = -i\pm (1+i)i\\ & = -i\pm(i-1)\\ & = -1\text{ or }-2i+1 \end{align} 
